### BudgetFlow API Collection
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080/api/v1
### Production URL: https://studycasebudgetflow-production.up.railway.app/api/v1

@base_url = https://studycasebudgetflow-production.up.railway.app/api/v1
@token = <paste-your-token-here>

## ============================================================
## AUTH
## ============================================================

### Register Manager
POST {{base_url}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Manager",
  "email": "john.manager@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "manager"
}

###

### Register Employee
POST {{base_url}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Employee",
  "email": "jane.employee@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "employee"
}

###

### Login as Finance
POST {{base_url}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "finance@budgetflow.id",
  "password": "Finance123!"
}

###

### Login as Manager
POST {{base_url}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "manager@budgetflow.id",
  "password": "Manager123!"
}

###

### Login as Employee
POST {{base_url}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "employee@budgetflow.id",
  "password": "Employee123!"
}

###

### Refresh Token
POST {{base_url}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh_token": "<paste-your-refresh-token-here>"
}

###

### Get Balance
GET {{base_url}}/me/balance
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

## ============================================================
## TOPUPS
## ============================================================

###

### Create Topup (Manager)
POST {{base_url}}/topups
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "amount": 10000000
}

###

### Review Topup - Approve (Finance)
# Replace <topup_public_id> with actual public_id from create response
# Idempotency-Key header prevents duplicate processing on retries
POST {{base_url}}/topups/<topup_public_id>/review
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}

{
  "status": "approved"
}

###

### List My Topups (Manager)
GET {{base_url}}/me/topups
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

## ============================================================
## PROJECTS
## ============================================================

###

### Create Project (Manager)
POST {{base_url}}/projects
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Website Redesign",
  "claim_amount": 500000,
  "envelope_total": 5000000
}

###

### List Projects
GET {{base_url}}/projects?page=1&limit=10&sort=-created_at
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### List Projects with Filter
GET {{base_url}}/projects?status=open&search=website&sort=title
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get Project Detail
# Replace <project_public_id> with actual public_id
GET {{base_url}}/projects/<project_public_id>
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Delete Project - Soft Delete (Manager)
# Replace <project_public_id> with actual public_id
DELETE {{base_url}}/projects/<project_public_id>
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Restore Project (Manager)
# Replace <project_public_id> with actual public_id
POST {{base_url}}/projects/<project_public_id>/restore
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

## ============================================================
## CLAIMS
## ============================================================

###

### Create Claim (Employee)
# Replace <project_public_id> with actual public_id
POST {{base_url}}/projects/<project_public_id>/claims
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "receipt_url": "https://storage.example.com/receipts/receipt-001.pdf"
}

###

### Review Claim - Approve (Finance or Manager)
# Replace <claim_public_id> with actual public_id
POST {{base_url}}/claims/<claim_public_id>/review
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}

{
  "status": "approved"
}

###

### List My Claims (Employee)
GET {{base_url}}/me/claims
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

## ============================================================
## PAYOUTS
## ============================================================

###

### Create Payout (Employee)
POST {{base_url}}/payouts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "amount": 500000
}

###

### Review Payout - Complete (Finance)
# Replace <payout_public_id> with actual public_id
POST {{base_url}}/payouts/<payout_public_id>/review
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}

{
  "status": "completed"
}

###

### Review Payout - Fail (Finance)
# Replace <payout_public_id> with actual public_id
POST {{base_url}}/payouts/<payout_public_id>/review
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}

{
  "status": "failed"
}

###

### List My Payouts (Employee)
GET {{base_url}}/payouts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
